HEADWORD: Epigrammatical
<hw>Ep`i*gram*mat"ic*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw><ety>[L.
<ets>epigrammaticus</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>⟦eacute⟧pigrammatique</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Writing
